This folder (csci596-as05) contains instruction and codes needed to complete assignment 5
for CSCI 596.

as05.pdf: Assignment.

pmd.c, pmd.h, pmd.in: MPI program, header file, and input parameter file for parallel
molecular dynamics (MD) as a potential starting point. However, you are encouraged
instead to use your pmd_irecv.c from assignment 4.

hmd.sl: Slurm script for part I: program verification.

hmd-scale.sl: Slurm script for part II: scalability test. It assumes that executables
named hmd1, hmd2, hmd4 and hmd8 have been compiled for 1, 2 4 and 8-threads, 
respectively.
